quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  8,59,"Kandi rwose ba bandi bahakanye ntibibwire ko bacitse (ibihano). Mu by'ukuri, ntibazananira (Allah)"
  8,60,"Kandi mubitegure n’imbaraga zanyu zose n’amafarasi yambariye intambara, kugira ngo bitere ubwoba abanzi ba Allah ndetse n’abanzi banyu n’abandi mutazi ariko bazwi na Allah. Kandi icyo mutanze cyose mu nzira ya Allah, mukigororerwa cyuzuye ndetse ntimuzahuguzwa"
  8,61,"Ariko nibahitamo inzira y’amahoro, na we uzayigane kandi wiringire Allah. Mu by’ukuri ni We Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  8,62,"Kandi nibashaka kukuryarya, mu by’ukuri, Allah araguhagije. Ni We waguteye inkunga y’ubutabazi bwe n’iy’abemeramana"
  8,63,"(Allah) yanahuje imitima yabo (nyuma y’uko bari batatanye). N’iyo wari gutanga ibiri mu isi byose, ntiwari gushobora guhuza imitima yabo (abemeramana). Ariko Allah yarayihuje. Mu by’ukuri We ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  8,64,Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Allah n’abemeramana bagukurikiye baraguhagije